    "body": "Commit [9476378](https://github.com/PaulRBerg/buidler/commit/94763780b8b718259374f5c6051a0a788a2897d2) fixed this. The issue had to do with a bogus `.call` function:\r\n\r\n```ts\r\ncreateFixtureLoader: buidlerCreateFixtureLoader.bind(buidlerWaffleProvider),\r\n```\r\n\r\nThad had to be changed to this:\r\n\r\n```ts\r\ncreateFixtureLoader: buidlerCreateFixtureLoader.bind(undefined, buidlerWaffleProvider),\r\n```\r\n\r\nThanks @alcuadrado for your support and for including the fix in [buidler-waffle@2.1.0](https://github.com/nomiclabs/buidler/releases/tag/buidler-waffle-v2.1.0).",
